  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study purpose is to evaluate efficacy of stress-reducing aromatherapy and learn about how
      aromatherapy works.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study purpose is to evaluate efficacy of stress-reducing aromatherapy and learn about how
      aromatherapy works by comparing participants' physiologic responses to laboratory challenge
      tasks with and without experiencing aromatherapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
